item.description: SoftLayer_Software_Component_Password Service Datatype Description This SoftLayer_Software_Component_Password data type contains a password for a specific software component instance. Local createDate The date this username/password pair was created. Type: dateTime id An id number for this specific username/password pair. Type: integer modifyDate The date of the last modification to this username/password pair. Type: dateTime notes A note string stored for this username/password pair.
